VASSAL.build.module

Class DoActionButton

  • java.lang.Object
    • VASSAL.build.AbstractBuildable
      • VASSAL.build.AbstractConfigurable
        • VASSAL.build.module.DoActionButton
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoConfigurable, Buildable, Configurable, PropertyNameSource, ValidityChecker, Translatable, RecursionLimiter.Loopable

    public class DoActionButton
extends AbstractConfigurable
implements RecursionLimiter.Loopable
    This component places a button into the controls window toolbar. Pressing the button displays a message, plays a sound and/or sends hotkeys
